%p
  A password reset request was issued for a user account signed up under this
  email address for <strong>#{@account.name}</strong>. To reset your password,
  follow the link below before #{@user.password_reset_sent_at.strftime("%m/%d/%Y at %-I:%M %p (%Z)")}.
  %br
  %br
  = link_to "https://keygen.sh/reset-password?token=#{@token}", "https://keygen.sh/reset-password?token=#{@token}", class: "ellipsis"
%p
  If you did not request your password to be reset, simply ignore this email and
  your password will continue to stay the same.
